Interface EntityWithLifecycle<I,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message>

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface EntityWithLifecycle<I,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
extends Entity<I,S>, WithLifecycle
    An entity which has lifecycle flags.

    Lifecycle flags determine if an entity is active. An entity is considered to be active if the lifecycle flags are missing. If an entity is archived or deleted, then itâ€™s regarded to be inactive.
